dct_title_s: [Kharitat al-Iraq]: nawahi Karkuk wa Tawuq wa al-Malhah
dct_description_sm: Iraq. Mudiriyat Amur al-Misaha. Iraq. Directorate of Surveying Affairs. [[Map of Iraq]: al-Malhah, Tawuq, and Karkuk sections.] Alternate title: Liwa' Karkuk: qada'ay Karkuk wa Tawuq: nawahy Karkuk wa Tawuq wa al-Malhah. [Karkuk province: Karkuk and Tawuq districts: Karkuk, Tawuq, and al-Malhah sections.] Relief shown by hachure, form lines, and contour lines at 1 meter intervals. Heights are shown with spot heights. Triangulation points are shown. Surveyed: 1937. Tribal lands and land ownership are shown.
